arts.ttl: Inaki Williams' 2 goals lead Bilbao to 2-0 win over Fenerbahce in Europa League
arts.sum: Inaki Williams scored twice Wednesday to help Athletic Bilbao stay unbeaten in the Europa League with a 2-0 away win at 10-man Fenerbahce. All the 17 remaining Europa League games are scheduled for Thursday, when Lazio and Frankfurt could join Bilbao atop the standings with wins.
